Package com.linkedin.cubert.operator.cube

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CubeAggregator
    Interface that specifies aggregators for the CUBE operator.
    DupleCubeAggregator
    Interface that specifies aggregators for the CUBE operator that can rollup inner dimensions.
    EasyCubeAggregator
    Generic interface for all cube aggregators.
    ValueAggregator
    Stateless aggregator of values.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CountDistinctCubeAggregator
    A memory-efficient implementation of [SUM, COUNT_TO_ONE] DupleCubeAggregator, for the special case when the aggregated column is known to be never null.
    CubeDimensions
    Manages the dimensions for the CUBE operator.
    DefaultCubeAggregator
    Builtin default implementation of a CubeAggregator that aggregates input columns using a specified ValueAggregator.
    DefaultDupleCubeAggregator
    Builtin default implementation of a DupleCubeAggregator that aggregates input columns using inner and outer ValueAggregator.
    DimensionKey
    Specifies the dimension columns.
    EasyCubeAggregatorBridge
    A bridge class that wraps user-defined aggregation functions (UDAFs) written with EasyCubeAggregator interface into DupleCubeAggregator interface.
    ValueAggregatorFactory
    Factory class for creating ValueAggregator.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ValueAggregationType
    Various types of built-in aggregators.
